{"tid":986434,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］日本iTunes 問題","createTime":"2019-01-18T12:17:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T13:06:50.000Z","uid":97958,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b322def90635923ce1c3da4e0629708fbc0e16a1","tid":986434,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:17:00.000Z","msg":"小弟係好耐之前已經開左日本iTunes AC<br />\n岩岩買左張日本iTunes 儲值卡<br />\n都成功入左儲值卡 係iTunes 睇到個金額<br />\n<br />\n但係<br />\n<br />\n當我要係隻game課金個陣<br />\n就彈出左以下問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ttuL2mk.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FttuL2mk.png&h=8dbd635d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入左去之後就係咁既畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4Ne4ytc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4Ne4ytc.png&h=0c075227&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我唔記得左自己set左乜野<br />\n<br />\n想問各英雄可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔想浪費左啲錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"682b8ecebccc77050fb50da526c43b93ab8d1304","tid":986434,"uid":136002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-18T12:17:37.000Z","msg":"打去apple reset <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d628424b65dbb47b287da321573306a96f67ab1","tid":986434,"uid":97958,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"682b8ecebccc7